      "role": "user",
      "content": "everything is just so quiet now. i walk into the kitchen and i still expect to see him sitting there, but then it hits me all over again that he’s actually gone. the house feels like a tomb. i don't see the point in waking up tomorrow just to sit in this silence again. it's like the color has just been bled out of everything.",
