    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not just feeling overwhelmed. it's like... the silence is heavy. it's constant. i look at his empty chair and it feels more real than anything else in this world. honestly, sometimes i feel like i'm just a ghost haunting this house, waiting for something to happen that i know isn't coming. it feels so irrational to keep fighting to stay in a world where he doesn't exist.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
