      "content": "I can't imagine how hard this must be for you. Grieving is a deeply personal journey and there's no right or wrong way to feel or heal. You’re not alone in this. Remember that it’s okay to take pauses and reflect when you need to. Take things one moment at a time. If you need to share your feelings, reach out to trusted friends, family, or a mental health professional for support. You're stronger than you realize.",
